    <div class="guide-content wow-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">Why Shadow?</div>
        <div class="panel-content">
            <p>Shadow Priests are one of the most desirable raid specs in TBC Classic. While your personal DPS is moderate, Vampiric Touch returns mana to your entire group equal to 5% of your Shadow damage, making you essential for sustaining mana-hungry casters. Shadow Weaving also increases Shadow damage taken by 10%, boosting Warlock DPS significantly. The 14/0/47 build maximizes Shadow output while picking up Meditation from Discipline for mana sustainability.</p>

            <h3>Key Talents</h3>
            <div class="talent-explanations">
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_shadowwordpain.jpg" alt="Vampiric Touch" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Vampiric Touch</h4>
                        <p>Causes Shadow damage over 15 sec. When the target takes damage from your Mind Blast, your party gains mana equal to 5% of the damage. The #1 reason you're brought to raids.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_shadowform.jpg" alt="Shadowform" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Shadowform</h4>
                        <p>Assume a Shadowform, increasing your Shadow damage by 15% and reducing Physical damage taken by 15%. Your core form for all Shadow DPS.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_misery.jpg" alt="Misery" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Misery</h4>
                        <p>Your Shadow Word: Pain, Mind Flay and Vampiric Touch spells also increase the chance for spells to hit by 5%. Massive raid-wide hit buff for all casters.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_shadowweaving.jpg" alt="Shadow Weaving" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Shadow Weaving</h4>
                        <p>Your Shadow damage spells have a 100% chance to cause your target to be vulnerable to Shadow damage, increasing Shadow damage taken by 2% per stack, up to 10%.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Stat Priority</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Hit Rating</strong> (until 16% / 202 rating for spells)</li>
                <li><strong>Spell Damage (Shadow)</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Spell Haste Rating</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Spell Critical Strike Rating</strong></li>
