        <div class="panel-content accordion-body">
            <p class="section-intro">Shadow Priest DPS follows a strict DoT-priority rotation. Keep Vampiric Touch and Shadow Word: Pain active at all times, use Mind Blast on cooldown to trigger mana return, and fill with Mind Flay. Shadow Word: Death is a filler when safe to use.</p>
            <ol class="rotation-list">
                <li>
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_shadowwordpain.jpg" alt="Vampiric Touch" class="rotation-icon" loading="lazy">
                    <div><span class="rotation-ability">Vampiric Touch</span> — Apply first and keep up at all times. When Mind Blast deals damage, your party gains mana equal to 5% of VT's damage.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_shadowwordpain.jpg" alt="Shadow Word: Pain" class="rotation-icon" loading="lazy">
                    <div><span class="rotation-ability">Shadow Word: Pain</span> — Keep up at all times. Strong DoT that benefits from Shadow Weaving and Shadow Form.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_unholyfrenzy.jpg" alt="Mind Blast" class="rotation-icon" loading="lazy">
                    <div><span class="rotation-ability">Mind Blast</span> — Use on cooldown (5.5s with talents). Triggers Vampiric Touch mana return for your group. Highest single-hit damage.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_siphonmana.jpg" alt="Mind Flay" class="rotation-icon" loading="lazy">
                    <div><span class="rotation-ability">Mind Flay</span> — Your primary filler. Cast 2-3 times between Mind Blast cooldowns. Clip the last tick if Mind Blast is coming off cooldown.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_shadow_demonicfortitude.jpg" alt="Shadow Word: Death" class="rotation-icon" loading="lazy">
                    <div><span class="rotation-ability">Shadow Word: Death</span> — Instant cast filler when safe. Deals backlash damage to you, so only use when healers can keep you topped.</div>
                </li>
